Package meico.midi

Classes and tools for representing and processing MIDI data.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EventMaker
    This helper class provides some useful midi-related functions.
    InstrumentsDictionary
    This is a helper class to parse a String to a program change number.
    Midi
    This class holds Midi data and provides som functionality for it.
    Midi2AudioRenderer
    This class is based on the Midi2WavRenderer class Karl Helgason and, thus, inherits the following copyright notice.
    Midi2MsmConverter
    This class does the MIDI to MSM conversion.
    MidiPlayer
    This class provides Midi playback functinality.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    UnsupportedSoundbankException
    Created by Axel Berndt on 19.09.2016.
